00:40:53,511 --> 00:40:57,893
or any kind of interaction with an enemy,

507
00:40:58,333 --> 00:41:01,234
you usually see, or you better see,

508
00:41:01,394 --> 00:41:04,775
a challenging peak followed by a foreseeable end.

509
00:41:04,895 --> 00:41:06,576
You can actually see where it's going to end.

510
00:41:07,877 --> 00:41:12,458
And a noticeable easing between them.

511
00:41:12,478 --> 00:41:15,760
And the idea of delta of chance is that, well,

512
00:41:15,820 --> 00:41:17,000
a positive delta of chance.

513
00:41:17,892 --> 00:41:21,433
puts you in a position where you see an anticipated failure and

514
00:41:21,693 --> 00:41:28,275
heightened risk followed by an anticipated triumph not immediate triumph, but anticipated triumph and

515
00:41:28,475 --> 00:41:29,475
that translates

516
00:41:30,475 --> 00:41:32,296
directly into the behavior of

517
00:41:33,436 --> 00:41:37,217
Dopamine now. I'm not a chemist a biochemist, but

